{"type": "article", "id": 18663, "title": "玻璃灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-08T07:41:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115153YhGWZPVALdDK4Mck.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组玻璃灯来自荷兰的设计工作室 VANTOT，玻璃灯罩的中间有一段是磨砂的，可以上下移动里面的灯泡来改变灯光的感觉。如果完全处于磨砂玻璃里面，就看不见灯泡的形状，光线显得朦胧，如果处在磨砂和透明之间，就有一个微妙的半隐半现的感觉。<a href=\"http://www.vantot.com/limpid-lights-vantot/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151513Y5e6N2mWcHjxaoD.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115151yL47zpljmNFOi5b2.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"899\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115152WxZ2vYQXlzhuLig7.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115152ZwQv9YueAqCDB04c.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115152AtgDw0aKp64QcMSq.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}